Vendor the Waydroid ARM translation payload here if you want fresh images to
seed libndk automatically.

Expected layout:

  /usr/share/batocera/waydroid/libndk/system/...
  /usr/share/batocera/waydroid/libndk/vendor/...

The helper /usr/bin/batocera-waydroid-arm will copy those files into:

  /var/lib/waydroid/overlay/system
  /var/lib/waydroid/overlay/vendor

and will update /var/lib/waydroid/waydroid.cfg with the required native bridge
and ABI properties for arm32 and arm64 app support.
